{"tid":2171715,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"取消SBA會唔會係考評局呢幾年最正確嘅決定？","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T07:22:45.000Z","uid":306528,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5bb09ec847e5acf7e82f5bae4e6a420d2d9133c7","tid":2171715,"uid":306528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:45:37.000Z","msg":"SBA個個都出貓就係人都知，一個唔好彩低分少少就足以令你冇咗粒星。<br />\n<br />\nSBA考嘅嘢又古古怪怪，最後變成問source擦鞋多過考你真實知識。<br />\n<br />\n好多人都會用「一試定生死」嚟形容冇SBA後嘅氣候，但以前舊制AL咪又係一試定生死。君不見~20% SBA足以分散DSE正卷嘅risk救學生一命，卻足以令high achiever 未考已經冤枉低1個grade。對好多考生而言，更係顧此失彼！<br />\n<br />\nHKEAA 近年不斷想cut syllabus，但其實取消SBA 已經減輕學生唔少負擔，更加能夠提高考試公平性。當然，取消SBA更加提高考生心理壓力要求，但我相信取消SBA必然係利多於弊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQqfJC1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQqfJC1.jpg&h=2e6e2901&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mHwuN4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmHwuN4H.jpg&h=5f66e033&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5108e8c3d4600640b8e67cbf96f62c4b0afb71ec","tid":2171715,"uid":198742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:07:58.000Z","msg":"早啲取消啦屌佢老母 大把人已經做完sba ies"},{"pid":"0198b9f52362025577667a39e4ddb2a861ae959a","tid":2171715,"uid":21661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"支持取消啦， <br />\nSba好無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}